Title: Baggage
Writer: Joseph Weisberg (created by), Joel Fields, Joseph Weisberg, Lara Shapiro (staff writer)
Actors: Keri Russell, Matthew Rhys, Lev Gorn, Annet Mahendru
Plot: Elizabeth and Philip come together to deal with a mission gone wrong, but struggle to reconcile their ideologies; Stan welcomes a Soviet defector to America; Nina acclimates to her new living arrangements.
